Interface Formats

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    AccessFormats, BatchProvider, Inputable, InputTranslatable, Outputable, OutputFormattable, OutputSerializable, RESTful
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ActionsEntityProviderMock, AnnouncementEntityProviderImpl, AssignmentEntityProviderImpl, ChatChannelEntityProvider, ChatMessageEntityProvider, EntityViewAccessProviderMock, ForumMessageEntityProviderImpl, ForumTopicEntityProviderImpl, MembershipEntityProvider, PCServiceEntityProvider, PollEntityProvider, PollOptionEntityProvider, PollVoteEntityProvider, ProfileEntityProvider, ProfileMessagingEntityProvider, ProfileStatusEntityProvider, RedirectableEntityProviderMock, RedirectControllableEntityProviderMock, RedirectDefineableEntityProviderMock, RequestStoreableEntityProviderMock, ResolvableEntityProviderMock, RESTfulEntityProviderMock, SearchEntityProvider, SerializeableEntityProviderMock, ServerConfigEntityProvider, SessionEntityProvider, SiteEntityProvider, SiteStatsMetricsEntityProvider, SynopticMsgcntrItemEntityProviderImpl, UserEntityProvider, UserPrefsEntityProvider

    public interface Formats
    Defines a list of possible format types (extensions) which can be handled and indicates which are handled internally
    Author:
    Aaron Zeckoski (aaron@caret.cam.ac.uk)
